transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]

Quickly and quietly, bring water to a boil in minutes from your countertop, desk, or office with the KitchenAid 5-cup electric kettle. The removable base, with 360 degree rotation, makes it easy to enjoy the perfect tea, hot chocolate, and more just about anywhere. And the spout, with removable lime scale filter, provides a precise pour. Expand your possibilities with the stylish, compact electric kettle, built to perform by KitchenAid.
